title: John Bel Edwards
added: Edwards is a [[Roman Catholic]]<ref name="Crisp"/> and a parishioner of the St. Helena Roman Catholic Church in Amite.<ref>[https://www.americamagazine.org/politics-society/2018/12/14/america-profile-louisiana-governor-john-bel-edwards-pro-life-catholic The America Profile: Louisiana Governor John Bel Edwards, the pro-life Catholic Democrat], ''[[America (magazine)|America]]'' (December 14, 2018).</ref> He is regularly seen attending church services at Christ the King Parish and Catholic Center, located on LSU's campus.
